# Ignore everything under .claude/ EXCEPT the shared project settings.json
# (ruff-on-edit PostToolUse hook) and the subagent definitions referenced by
# CLAUDE.md §11. settings.local.json + scratch stay ignored. Note: must use
# `.claude/*` not `.claude` — git cannot re-include a child of an excluded
# *directory*.
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
!.claude/agents/
Claude-plans.lnk

